      "text": [
        "2200 - وَ رُوِيَ : «أَنَّ مَنْ حَلَقَ رَأْسَهُ بِمِنًى كَانَ لَهُ بِكُلِّ شَعْرَةٍ نُورٌ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2200 - It has been narrated: \"Whoever shaves their head at Mina will have a light for every hair on the Day of Judgment.\""
        ]
      }
    }
